    ('FAUX FUR TRIM GILET', 'https://media.boohoo.com/i/boohoo/gzz80169_cream_xl/?qlt=80&fmt=auto', 'https://media.boohoo.com/i/boohoo/gzz80169_cream_xl_1/female-cream-faux-fur-trim-gilet', 'https://media.boohoo.com/i/boohoo/gzz80169_cream_xl_2/female-cream-faux-fur-trim-gilet', 'https://media.boohoo.com/i/boohoo/gzz80169_cream_xl_3/female-cream-faux-fur-trim-gilet', '', 70, 'Best Offer', 'It\s gilet season - the perfect companion for those colder days. A padded sleeveless jacket resembling a waistcoat design, our women\s gilets have got you covered this winter. Snug, sophisticated and always in style, team a fitted body warmer with a fresh crop top and high waisted mom jeans for a crisp autumnal look. Perfect for layering, grab your go-to heeled boots and faux leather trousers and slip into a shaggy faux fur gilet for snug winter wanders. Need something cosier for your off-duty days? Layer a padded style over your fave roll neck and joggers, and get ready to relax.', 'Women');
